Package suncertify.ui.listeners

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BookSubcontractorListener
    BookSubcontractorListener acts as the controller (MVC pattern) for the book button functionality.
    BrowseDatabaseButtonListener
    Common listener class for when the user clicks on the browse button in a config dialog.
    ClientOkButtonListener
    ClientOkButtonListener extends the abstract class OKButtonListener and is responsible for implementing the relevant methods in this class, such as validating configuration data entered by the user, saving config data to disk, and returning the correct business service for running in client mode.
    OKButtonListener
    OKButtonListener is an abstract class that should be implemented by the OK button listener of either the client or standalone configuration dialog classes.
    SearchSubcontractorListener
    SearchSubcontractorListener listens to events on the search button in the main application window.
    ServerOkButtonListener
    The ServerOkButtonListener does not extend the generic OKButtonListener class like the other OK button listeners.
    StandaloneOkButtonListener
    StandaloneOkButtonListener extends the abstract class OKButtonListener and is responsible for implementing the relevant methods in this class, such as validating configuration data entered by the user, saving config data to disk, and returning the correct business service for running in client mode.
